Roles & Responsibilities
We have openings for part-time positions for the role of Ecommerce Operations Executive (Part-Time). Flexible 2-5 days a week job.
Responsibilities
Manage & Update of the Online Store(s)
Manage & Process Online Orders;
Perform Quality Check on Stocks;
Manage Stocks, Showroom Display and Store & Office Supplies;
Prepare Management Reports:
Manage Social Media Accounts;
Provide Admin & Operational Support as required
Requirements:
Able to commit for minimum 6 months;
Meticulous, organized and with a good eye for details;
Proficient in MS Excel;
Good spoken/written English;
Singaporeans or PRs
Part-time tertiary students are welcome to apply.
Interested applicants, please email your resume with a recent photograph to career@pinkorchard.com.
Only resumes sent to career@pinkorchard.com will be reviewed.
Only shortlisted candidate will be notified.

