Roles & Responsibilities
Family hair salon looking to hire a part-time Receptionist to manage the front-of-house. Our salon is conveniently located at Forum Shopping Mall, within walking distance from Orchard MRT Station.

Duties & responsibilities include:
Greeting customers;
Directing customers to their preferred stylists;
Answering phone calls;
Cashiering duties;
Keeping basic inventory of products;
Administrative duties.
Training will be provided on our in-house and administrative procedures.

Working days are from Monday to Sunday, with weekends preferred. Flexible working day arrangement. (Students above 18 years are welcome to apply.)

Working hours are from 10.30am to 6.30pm.

Please note only shortlisted applicants will be contacted. Thank you!
